{"tid":2501151,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日防衛大臣：中国正在不顯眼處步步侵略","createTime":"2021-04-23T07:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T07:46:22.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7acf5676b632853ddd7b9f238117a82e359f23c1","tid":2501151,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:23:45.000Z","msg":"日本防衛大臣岸信夫在執政黨自民黨議員會議發表演講時指, 中國正在不顯眼之處步步侵略, 最終目的是改變現狀, 日本不能接受這個情況.<br />\n<br />\n        岸信夫在演講中提到, 中國海警船在釣魚台列島, 即日本稱的尖閣諸島活動, 以及在東海、南海等海域活動日趨頻繁.<br />\n<br />\n        對於台灣情況, 岸信夫指, 如果台灣被赤化, 將發生嚴重變化. 他重申希望台海兩岸的問題可以和平解決.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20210423144942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20210423144942&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzoeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=350ea30a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20210423144942</a>"},{"pid":"359d787eef2535629dc10dad56528e377ce8f81d","tid":2501151,"uid":292601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:24:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾原神都玩死你"},{"pid":"b21c4221b4b9a2551b6d9520676392fcfc31f47f","tid":2501151,"uid":345502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"359d787eef2535629dc10dad56528e377ce8f81d","tid":2501151,"uid":292601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:24:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾原神都玩死你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:42:24.000Z","msg":"真.<br />\n<br />\n連ACG呢條戰線都守唔住."},{"pid":"054f9620886686265e510881d01707dd60447c40","tid":2501151,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b21c4221b4b9a2551b6d9520676392fcfc31f47f","tid":2501151,"uid":345502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"359d787eef2535629dc10dad56528e377ce8f81d","tid":2501151,"uid":292601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:24:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾原神都玩死你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:42:24.000Z","msg":"真.<br />\n